            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I have 3 mistakes in my collection. One is a Snoppy with only half of his face painted MOC, one is a witch with no hat MOC, both I found myself, the other one I got on line from the ebay auction, it's a Mickey Mouse with only the background face, no nose, also MOC. I don't know how much their worth, there just interesting.</font>
          </td>
        </tr>
